summary: An Ordinance accepting the dedication of certain portions of Section Sixteen (16), Township Twenty-five (25) North, Range Four (4) East, W. M., in accordance with Chapter 37, Session Laws of 1909, and directing the Corporation Counsel to dismiss condemnation proceedings heretofore instituted in the Superior Court of King County, under Ordinance No. 17947, insofar as said proceedings affect such dedicated lands.
